Download and install VirtualBox: 
https://download.virtualbox.org/virtualbox/6.1.30/VirtualBox-6.1.30-148432-Win.exe

After installation, download the extension pack:
https://download.virtualbox.org/virtualbox/6.1.30/Oracle_VM_VirtualBox_Extension_Pack-6.1.30.vbox-extpack

Just double click the file and it'll install automatically

Now download the .ova for Kali Linux:
https://kali.download/virtual-images/kali-2021.4a/kali-linux-2021.4a-virtualbox-amd64.ova

Double click on the file and it'll open up in VirtualBox, all ready to set up. 

